sectionedDescription.description:
Boasting a convenient location in East Mesa, the property makes an excellent destination for those who love shopping, golfing, or just relaxing in a customer-oriented hotel environment. Discover the scenic views of Usery Mountain Regional Park or choose from various golf courses, including Desert Sands Golf Course and Coyote Run Golf Course. Both business and solo travelers love the property for its conducive amenities, cleanliness, and friendly staff.

A great pick if you are looking for a convenient location that is quiet but not too far out of the way. The pet-friendly hotel takes pride in superior customer service, and its amenities are designed to give you the comfort you need for a refreshing stay. All rooms are fully furnished, providing an environment conducive to a relaxing experience and action-oriented activities. Get off to a great start with a delectable breakfast and your favorite cup of coffee. Relax in the outdoor pool as you plan your day to get out and do some shopping or enjoy a game or an event at Hohokam Stadium or Bell Bank Park. Complimentary parking and WIFI are available. Additional facilities are fitness and business centers.

PLEASE NOTE:
- The maximum number of days that you may book per reservation is only 28 days.
- The listing is distributed and managed by RoomPicks Accommodations.

THE UNIT

This 463sf unit features:
- 1 King bed;
- Daily housekeeping;
- Flat-screen TV with premium channels;
- Pool view;
- Coffee maker, fridge, microwave;
- Ironing facilities;
- All linens, towels, and bathroom essentials are provided. You don’t need to bring a thing!!

THE PROPERTY

Our family-friendly property provides the following on-site amenities:
- 24/7 Front desk and Security;
- Swimming pool;
- Hot tub;
- Free continental breakfast available daily 7:30 AM–10:00 AM;
- Fitness center;
- Business center;
- Meeting room;
- Mini market;
- Vending machine;
- Pets allowed for an extra charge of USD 25.00 per accommodation, per day, 2 per room;
- Parking is available for guests on the property and is free of cost (for 1 car per unit).

