sectionedDescription.description:
Our hotel, which is located in Manhattan, aims to give visitors a sense of a home away from home. The American Dream, Bronx Zoo, Times Square, Rockefeller Center, and One World Trade Center are just a few miles away from the hotel, and each offers fun things to keep visitors entertained while they are there. The suites are a great option for unwinding and relaxing because the subdued elegance of our hotel envelops each visitor with comfort and seclusion.

To ensure that visitors are comfortable, our hotel has several amenities and conveniences. Each of the tastefully decorated rooms has a contemporary and fashionable air, and it is furnished with all the comforts of home. A variety of treatments and services are available at the on-site spa and fitness facility to aid clients in relaxing and unwinding. The hotel's restaurant offers a selection of regional and international cuisine to suit every palate. Additionally, there is a bar there where you may unwind with a drink. With an onsite business center, business travelers are offered the utmost convenience and service for an enjoyable and stress-free stay. 

PLEASE NOTE: 
- Please note that the resort fee is not included in the daily rate. A mandatory resort fee of $48.99/day/unit plus tax will be collected upon arrival.
- The listing is distributed and managed by RoomPicks Accommodations. 
- The maximum number of days that you may book per reservation is only 28 days.

THE UNIT

This 2195sf Duplex Terrace Suite features:
- 1 King Bed;
- Daily housekeeping;
- Coffee maker, Mini fridge, microwave;
- LCD TV;
- Air conditioning;
- Minibar;
- Ironing facilities;
- Safety deposit box;
- Desk;
- All linens, towels, and bathroom essentials are provided. You don’t need to bring a thing!

THE PROPERTY

Our family-friendly property provides the following on-site amenities:
- 24/7 Front desk and Security;
- On-site restaurant and bar;
- Fitness center;
- Business center;
- Mini market;
- ATM/cash machine on site;
- Happy hour (for a charge);
- Laundry facilities;
- Babysitting/child services;
- Currency exchange;
- Pet bowls;
- Grocery deliveries (for a charge);
- Facilities for disabled guests;
- Spa and wellness area;
- Dogs are allowed on request. No extra charges. Up to 60 lbs per pet;
- Valet parking is available and costs USD 65 per day.

